ut employment tribunals from the Citizen’s Advice Bureau", :cy=>"Get advice about employment tribunals from the Citizen’s Advice Bureau", :url=>"http://www.citizensadvice.org.uk/index/getadvice"}, 56=>{:en=>"Talk to your local health centre and pharmacy", :cy=>"Siaradwch â’ch canolfan iechyd a fferyllfa leol", :url=>""}, 57=>{:en=>"Speak to HM Revenue & Customs on their Tax Credit Helpline on 0345 300 3900", :cy=>"Siaradwch â Chyllid a Thollau EM ar eu Llinell Gymorth Credyd Treth ar 0345 300 3900", :url=>""}, 58=>{:en=>"Talk to your employer", :cy=>"Siaradwch â’ch cyflogwr", :url=>""}, 59=>{:en=>"Speak to HM Revenue & Customs on their Child Benefit Helpline on 0845 302 1444", :cy=>"Siaradwch â Chyllid a Thollau EM ar eu Llinell Gymorth Budd-dal Plant ar 0845 302 1444", :url=>""}, 60=>{:en=>"Find your local Jobcentre Plus", :cy=>"", :url=>"http://los.direct.gov.uk/default.aspx?type=1&lang=en"}, 61=>{:en=>"The Social Fund may be able to help with funeral expenses if you're on low income", :cy=>"Efallai y bydd y Gronfa Gymdeithasol yn gallu helpu â threuliau angladd os ydych ar incwm isel", :url=>""}, 62=>{:en=>"If you do not earn enough to claim Statutory Sick Pay or your Statutory Sick Pay runs out, you may be entitled to Employment and Support Allowance", :cy=>"If you do not earn enough to claim Statutory Sick Pay or your Statutory Sick Pay runs out, you may be entitled to Employment and Support Allowance", :url=>"http://www.direct.gov.uk/en/MoneyTaxAndBenefits/BenefitsTaxCreditsAndOtherSupport/Illorinjured/DG_171894"}, 63=>{:en=>"You can find out more about claiming Statutory Sick Pay on the Gov.uk website", :cy=>"Cewch wybod mwy am hawlio Tâl Salwch Statudol ar wefan Gov.uk", :url=>"https://www.gov.uk/statutory-sick-pay-ssp"}, 64=>{:en=>"Find your local Jobcentre Plus", :cy=>"", :url=>"http://los.direct.gov.uk/default.aspx?type=1&lang=en"}, 65=>{:en=>"You can also contact the HM Revenue & Customs employee helpline directly on 0845 302 1479", :cy=>"Gallwch hefyd gysylltu â Llinell Gymorth Cyflogeion Cyllid a Thollau EM yn uniongyrchol ar 0845 302 1479", :url=>""}, 66=>{:en=>"The Directgov website is a good starting point for information if you think your employer's decision is wrong", :cy=>"Mae gwefan Directgov yn fan cychwyn da i gael gwybodaeth os ydych yn meddwl bod penderfyniad eich cyflogwr yn anghywir", :url=>""}, 67=>{:en=>"To find an IFA in your area see the unbiased.co.uk website", :cy=>"To find an IFA in your area see the unbiased.co.uk website", :url=>"http://www.unbiased.co.uk"}, 68=>{:en=>"Just ask your pharmacist for a receipt and a claim form FP57. At your dentist, it's form FP64", :cy=>"Gofynnwch i’ch fferyllydd am dderbynneb a ffurflen hawlio FP57. Gyda’ch deintydd, ffurflen FP64 yw hi", :url=>""}, 69=>{:en=>"Contact the student support or welfare officer at your college or speak to a guidance teacher at school", :cy=>"Cysylltwch â’r swyddog cymorth i fyfyrwyr neu swyddog lles yn eich coleg neu siaradwch ag athro bugeiliol yn yr ysgol", :url=>""}, 70=>{:en=>"Call the Tax Credit Helpline on 0345 300 3900", :cy=>"Ffoniwch y Llinell Gymorth Credydau Treth ar 0345 300 3900", :url=>""}, 71=>{:en=>"To find out what is classed as registered or approved childcare for tax credits, see the Gov.uk website", :cy=>"I gael gwybod beth sy'n cael ei ystyried yn ofal plant cofrestredig neu gymeradwy ar gyfer talebau gofal plant, ewch i wefan Gov.uk", :url=>"https://www.gov.uk/childcare-tax-credits/registered-or-approved-childcare"}, 72=>{:en=>"Call the Tax Credits Helpline on 0345 300 3900 for information and advice about what you might be entitled to", :cy=>"Ffoniwch y Llinell Gymorth Credydau Treth ar 0345 300 3900 i gael gwybodaeth a chyngor am yr hyn y gallech chi fod â hawl i'w gael", :url=>""}, 73=>{:en=>"Speak to your company's HR Department to discuss your options for salary sacrifice and what's best for you", :cy=>"Siaradwch ag Adran Adnoddau Dynol eich cwmni i drafod eich opsiynau ar gyfer aberthu cyflog a’r hyn sydd orau i chi", :url=>""}, 74=>{:en=>"To find out what is classed as registered or approved childcare for tax credits, see the Gov.uk website", :cy=>"I gael gwybod beth sy'n cael ei ystyried yn ofal plant cofrestredig neu gymeradwy ar gyfer talebau gofal plant, ewch i wefan Gov.uk", :url=>"https://www.gov.uk/childcare-tax-credits/eligibility"}, 75=>{:en=>"Speak to your boss or the company's HR Department to find out what childcare help is available", :cy=>"Siaradwch â’ch rheolwr neu Adran AD y cwmni i gael gwybod pa gymorth sydd ar gael gyda gofal plant", :url=>""}, 76=>{:en=>"Use the table below to check if you're entitled to benefits and then make your claim as soon as possible", :cy=>"Defnyddiwch y tabl isod i weld a oes gennych chi hawl i fudd-daliadau ac wedyn hawlio cyn gynted â phosibl", :url=>""}, 77=>{:en=>"For a complete run-down of tax credit rules when you're on maternity leave, visit the HM Revenue & Customs website or call the Tax Credits helpline on 0345 300 3900", :cy=>"For a complete run-down of tax credit rules when you're on maternity leave, visit the HM Revenue & Customs website or call the Tax Credits helpline on 0345 300 3900", :url=>"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/taxcredits/keep-up-to-date/changes-affect/family-change/maternity-adoption.htm"}, 78=>{:en=>"Check out the Directgov website to find out more about claiming tax credits when you have a new baby", :cy=>"", :url=>"http://www.direct.gov.uk/en/MoneyTaxAndBenefits/TaxCredits/Keepingyourtaxcreditsuptodate/Changesthataffectyourtaxcredits/Familychanges/DG_172968"}, 79=>{:en=>"Use the Tax credit calculator on the HM Revenue & Customs website to see if you're eligible for tax credits and to get a rough idea how much you could get", :cy=>"Use the Tax credit calculator on the HM Revenue & Customs website to see if you're eligible for tax credits and to get a rough idea how much you could get", :url=>"http://taxcredits.hmrc.gov.uk/Qualify/DIQHousehold.aspx"}, 80=>{:en=>"Phone the Pension Service helpline on 0845 606 0265 to talk it through with an adviser", :cy=>"Ffoniwch linell gymorth y Gwasanaeth Pensiwn ar 0845 606 0265 i gael sgwrs am hyn gyda chynghorydd", :url=>""}, 81=>{:en=>"Download the Child Benefit claim form from the HM Revenue & Customs website", :cy=>"Download the Child Benefit claim form from the HM Revenue & Customs website", :url=>"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/forms/ch2-online-stubb.htm"}, 82=>{:en=>"If you're not sure you can claim, check the HM Revenue & Customs website ", :cy=>"Os nad ydych yn siŵr y gallwch ei hawlio, gwiriwch wefan Cyllid a Thollau EM", :url=>"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/childbenefit/start/who-qualifies/do-you-qualify.htm"}, 83=>{:en=>"Find out more about Employment and Support Allowance on the Gov.uk website or call 0800 055 6688", :cy=>"Dewch o hyd i ragor am Lwfans Cyflogaeth a Chymorth ar wefan Gov.uk neu ffoniwch nhw ar 0800 055 6688", :url=>"https://www.gov.uk/employment-support-allowance#overview"}, 84=>{:en=>"Download a claim form from the Gov.uk website", :cy=>"Llwytho ffurflen i lawr oddi ar wefan Gov.uk", :url=>"https://www.gov.uk/maternity-allowance"}, 85=>{:en=>"Call Jobcentre Plus on 0800 055 6688", :cy=>"Ffoniwch y Ganolfan Byd Gwaith ar 0800 055 6688", :url=>""}, 86=>{:en=>"Get a claim form from your local Jobcentre Plus", :cy=>"Get a claim form from your local Jobcentre Plus", :url=>"http://los.direct.gov.uk/default.aspx?type=1&amp;lang=en"}, 87=>{:en=>"Find out more about who qualifies for Maternity Allowance on the Directgov website", :cy=>"Ewch i wefan Directgov i gael gwybod mwy am bwy sy’n gymwys i gael Lwfans Mamolaeth", :url=>""}, 88=>{:en=>"For more information about making a complaint, including how to register your dispute with HM Revenue & Customs see the Directgov website", :cy=>"", :url=>"http://www.direct.gov.uk/en/MoneyTaxAndBenefits/BenefitsTaxCreditsAndOtherSupport/Illorinjured/DG_178466"}, 89=>{:en=>"Find out more about Statutory Maternity Leave on the Directgov website", :cy=>"Find out more about Statutory Maternity Leave on the Directgov website", :url=>"http://www.direct.gov.uk/en/Parents/Moneyandworkentitlements/WorkAndFamilies/Pregnancyandmaternityrights/DG_10039631"}, 90=>{:en=>"Give your employer your maternity certificate (form MATB1) signed by your doctor or midwife as evidence of when your baby's due. Without it, your employer can legitimately decide not to pay Statutory Maternity Pay", :cy=>"Rhowch eich tystysgrif mamolaeth (ffurflen MATB1) wedi ei llofnodi gan eich meddyg neu fydwraig i’ch cyflogwr fel tystiolaeth o ddyddiad geni disgwyliedig eich babi. Hebddi, gall eich cyflogwr benderfynu yn gyfreithlon nad yw am dalu Tâl Mamolaeth Statudo", :url=>""}, 91=>{:en=>"Tell your employer that you're pregnant and when the baby's due. You might have to do this in writing", :cy=>"Dywedwch wrth eich cyflogwr eich bod yn feichiog a phryd y disgwylir i’r babi gael ei eni. Efallai y bydd raid i chi wneud hyn yn ysgrifenedig", :url=>""}, 92=>{:en=>"Check with your employer, HR department or trade union, or look over your contract of employment, for details of the company's maternity pay scheme", :cy=>"Holwch eich cyflogwr, yr adran adnoddau dynol neu undeb llafur, neu edrychwch ar eich cytundeb cyflogaeth, am fanylion cynllun tâl mamolaeth y cwmni", :url=>""}, 93=>{:en=>"Use the Benefits adviser tool on the Gov.uk website to find out what benefits and tax credits you may be entitled to", :cy=>"", :url=>"https://www.gov.uk/benefits-adviser"}, 94=>{:en=>"You can download a claim pack and get more information from the Gov.uk website", :cy=>"Gallwch lawrlwytho pecyn cais a chael rhagor o wybodaeth o wefan Gov.uk", :url=>"https://www.gov.uk/sure-start-maternity-grant"}, 95=>{:en=>"To get a claim pack, contact your nearest Jobcentre Plus", :cy=>"", :url=>"http://los.direct.gov.uk/default.aspx"}, 96=>{:en=>"For more information and to check if you qualify, go to the Healthy Start website", :cy=>"Am fwy o wybodaeth ac i weld a ydych yn gymwys, ewch i wefan Cychwyn Iach", :url=>"http://www.healthystart.nhs.uk/healthy-start-vouchers/do-i-qualify/"}, 97=>{:en=>"Start putting away as much money as you can to buy yourself time after the baby is born", :cy=>"Dechreuwch roi cymaint o arian o’r neilltu ag y gallwch i brynu amser ichi’ch hunan ar ôl i’r babi gael ei eni", :url=>""}, 98=>{:en=>"Give your employer as much notice as possible of your antenatal appointments to help with work planning", :cy=>"Rhowch gymaint o rybudd â phosibl i’ch cyflogwr am eich apwyntiadau cynenedigol i’w helpu i gynllunio gwaith", :url=>""}, 99=>{:en=>"Look at your contract or talk to your boss or human resources department to find out how much Maternity Pay you're entitled to", :cy=>"Edrychwch ar eich contract neu siaradwch â’ch pennaeth neu adran adnoddau dynol er mwyn canfod faint o Dâl Mamolaeth y mae gennych hawl iddo", :url=>""}, 100=>{:en=>"Use the Maternity rights calculator on the Directgov website to find out what statutory pay and leave you're entitled to", :cy=>"Defnyddiwch y Gyfrifiannell hawliau mamolaeth ar wefan Directgov i ganfod pa dâl ac absenoldeb statudol y mae gennych hawl iddynt", :url=>"http://www.direct.gov.uk/maternity.dsb"}, 101=>{:en=>"Read the Gov.uk guide to becoming self-employed", :cy=>"Darllenwch y canllaw Gov.uk ar fod yn hunangyflogedig", :url=>"https://www.gov.uk/become-self-employed"}, 102=>{:en=>"Read the HMRC guide for casual workers", :cy=>"Read the HMRC guide for casual workers", :url=>"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/working/intro/casual.htm"}, 103=>{:en=>"Use the Childcare indicator calculator on the HM Revenue & Customs website to help you work out your best option for paying for childcare", :cy=>"Use the Childcare indicator calculator on the HM Revenue & Customs website to help you work out your best option for paying for childcare", :url=>"http://ccincalculator.hmrc.gov.uk/CCIN0.aspx"}, 104=>{:en=>"Tell your employer when you want to start your maternity leave at least 15 weeks before the beginning of the week when your baby is due", :cy=>"Dywedwch wrth eich cyflogwr pryd rydych eisiau dechrau’ch absenoldeb mamolaeth o leiaf 15 wythnos cyn dechrau’r wythnos y tybir y bydd eich babi’n cael ei eni", :url=>""}, 105=>{:en=>"Let your employer know when you intend to start maternity leave. You must tell them at least 15 weeks before your expected due date", :cy=>"Gadewch i’ch cyflogwr wybod pryd yr ydych yn bwriadu cychwyn eich absenoldeb mamolaeth. Rhaid ichi ddweud wrthyn nhw o leiaf 15 wythnos cyn eich dyddiad geni disgwyliedig", :url=>""}, 106=>{:en=>"Tell your employer when you want your maternity pay to start, giving them at least 28 days' notice. If you don't (and you don't have a reasonable excuse), your employer can refuse to pay Statutory Maternity Pay", :cy=>"Dywedwch wrth eich cyflogwr pryd yr ydych am i’ch tâl mamolaeth gychwyn, gan roi o leiaf 28 diwrnod o rybudd iddo. Os na fyddwch yn gwneud hynny (ac nad oes gennych reswm rhesymol), gall eich cyflogwr wrthod talu Tâl Mamolaeth Statudol", :url=>""}, 107=>{:en=>"Open a bank account to receive your payments if you don't already have one", :cy=>"Agorwch gyfrif banc i dderbyn eich taliadau os nad oes un gennych chi eisoes", :url=>""}, 108=>{:en=>"Call the Tax Credits helpline on 0345 300 3900 to let them know about any changes to your circumstances", :cy=>"Ffoniwch y Llinell Gymorth Credydau Treth ar 0345 300 3900 i roi gwybod iddyn nhw am unrhyw newid yn eich amgylchiadau", :url=>""}, 109=>{:en=>"Use the Tax credits calculator on the HM Revenue & Customs website to find out if you qualify and get a rough idea of how much you could be entitled to", :cy=>"Use the Tax credits calculator on the HM Revenue & Customs website to find out if you qualify and get a rough idea of how much you could be entitled to", :url=>"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/taxcredits/questionnaires.htm"}, 110=>{:en=>"Fill out the Maternity Exemption form (FW8). It’s available from your doctor or midwife. They’ll sign and send it in and you’ll receive your certificate in the post", :cy=>"Llenwch y ffurflen Eithrio Mamolaeth (FW8). Mae ar gael gan eich meddyg neu fydwraig. Byddant yn ei llofnodi a’i hanfon i mewn i chi a byddwch yn derbyn eich tystysgrif yn y post", :url=>""}, 111=>{:en=>"Ask your employer for written confirmation that your pension contributions are being paid", :cy=>"Gofynnwch i’ch cyflogwr am gadarnhad ysgrifenedig bod eich cyfraniadau pensiwn yn cael eu talu", :url=>""}, 112=>{:en=>"Report an employer to HMRC for avoiding tax", :cy=>"", :url=>"http://www.direct.gov.uk/en/MoneyTaxAndBenefits/Taxes/ContactOrDealWithHMRC/DG_10010579"}, 113=>{:en=>"Read more about paying tax on employee benefits on the HMRC website", :cy=>"Read more about paying tax on employee benefits on the HMRC website", :url=>"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/working/bens-shares-tips/benefits.htm"}, 114=>{:en=>"Find out about your responsibilities from the Landlord Law Blog website", :cy=>"Find out about your responsibilities from the Landlord Law Blog website", :url=>"http://www.landlordlawblog.co.uk/2010/08/24/landlord-responsibilities-what-being-a-landlord-really-means/"}, 115=>{:en=>"Find out about the process of buying to let, and what you should consider before you buy, from the Council of Mortgage Lenders website", :cy=>"Find out about the process of buying to let, and what you should consider before you buy, from the Council of Mortgage Lenders website", :url=>"http://www.cml.org.uk/cml/consumers/guides/buytolet"}, 116=>{:en=>"Set up annual and in-year review dates for my savings", :cy=>"Sefydlu dyddiadau blynyddol ac yn ystod y flwyddyn ar gyfer adolygu fy nghynilion", :url=>""}, 117=>{:en=>"Carry out annual savings and investment changes", :cy=>"Gwnewch newidiadau'n flynyddol i'ch cynilion a'ch buddsoddiadau", :url=>""}, 118=>{:en=>"Tell HMRC about any changes to your employee benefits", :cy=>"Tell HMRC about any changes to your employee benefits", :url=>"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/dealingwith/reporting-changes.htm#5"}, 119=>{:en=>"For exact figures, use the HM Revenue & Customs calculator", :cy=>"For exact figures, use the HM Revenue & Customs calculator", :url=>"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/calcs/ccin.htm"}, 120=>{:en=>"If you do decide to go ahead and work for yourself, register as self-employed on the HM Revenue & Customs website", :cy=>"Os ydych yn penderfynu mynd ymlaen a gweithio drosoch eich hun, cofrestrwch fel person hunangyflogedig ar wefan Cyllid a Thollau EM", :url=>"https://online.hmrc.gov.uk/shortforms/form/CWF1ST?dept-name=CWF1&sub-dept"}, 121=>{:en=>"Find out more about starting up and running a business on the Gov.uk website", :cy=>"Darganfyddwch ragor am gychwyn a rhedeg busnes ar y wefan Gov.uk ", :url=>"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business"}, 122=>{:en=>"If you're ready to fight your spending together, look at the Stop spending section on the MoneySavingExpert website", :cy=>"If you're ready to fight your spending together, look at the Stop spending section on the MoneySavingExpert website", :url=>"http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/family/stop-spending-budgeting-tool"}, 123=>{:en=>"If spiralling debt is the main problem, call the free National Debtline on 0808 808 4000 for help", :cy=>"Os mai dyled gynyddol yw’r brif broblem, ffoniwch y Llinell Ddyled Genedlaethol rhad ac am ddim ar 0808 808 4000 am help", :url=>""}, 124=>{:en=>"For advice from a relationship counsellor, contact Relate on 0300 100 1234 to talk things through with someone, although you will probably have to pay for sessions with a counsellor", :cy=>"Am gyngor gan gwnselydd perthynas, cysylltwch â Relate ar 0300 100 1234 i drafod pethau â rhywun, er y bydd angen i chi dalu mae'n debyg am sesiynau gyda chwnselydd", :url=>""}, 125=>{:en=>"Go to the Child maintenance calculator on the CM Options website to see how much you could expect to pay or receive", :cy=>"Ewch i’r Gyfrifiannell cynhaliaeth plant ar wefan Opsiynau Cynhaliaeth Plant i weld faint allech chi ddisgwyl ei dalu neu ei dderbyn", :url=>"http://www.cmoptions.org/en/calculator/calculator.asp"}, 126=>{:en=>"Get more information on family-based arrangements and download a form to record what you've agreed on the CM Options website", :cy=>"Ewch i’r wefan Opsiynau Cynhaliaeth Plant i gael rhagor o wybodaeth ar drefniadau teuluol a lawrlwytho ffurflen i gofnodi beth ydych wedi ei gytuno", :url=>"http://www.cmoptions.org/en/toolbox/negotiations.asp#page=page-1"}, 127=>{:en=>"Get more information about using the Child Support Agency on the CM Options website", :cy=>"Get more information about using the Child Support Agency on the CM Options website", :url=>"http://www.cmoptions.org/en/options/child-support-agency.asp"}, 128=>{:en=>"Follow the step-by-step guide on the CM Options website to set up a CSA maintenance arrangement", :cy=>"Follow the step-by-step guide on the CM Options website to set up a CSA maintenance arrangement", :url=>"http://www.cmoptions.org/en/options/child-support-agency-application.asp"}, 129=>{:en=>"Go to the CM Options website for information about using the courts to arrange child maintenance", :cy=>"Dysgwch fwy am ddefnyddio’r llysoedd i drefnu cynhaliaeth plant ar wefan Opsiynau Cynhaliaeth Plant", :url=>"http://www.cmoptions.org/en/other-arrangements/consent-orders-minutes-of-agreement.asp"}, 130=>{:en=>"Make a will or review the one you have to make sure your partner and children get what you want them to", :cy=>"Gwnewch ewyllys neu adolygwch yr un sydd gennych i wneud yn siŵr y bydd eich partner a'ch plant yn cael yr hyn rydych yn dymuno iddynt ei gael", :url=>""}, 131=>{:en=>"Speak to your guidance teacher at school, or contact the student support or welfare officer at your college or university. They'll have a clear picture of what help is available there you live and how to apply for it", :cy=>"Siaradwch â’ch athro bugeiliol yn yr ysgol, neu cysylltwch â’r swyddog cymorth i fyfyrwyr neu'r swyddog lles yn eich coleg neu'ch prifysgol. Bydd ganddynt ddarlun clir o’r cymorth sydd ar gael lle rydych yn byw a sut i wneud cais amdano", :url=>""}, 132=>{:en=>"Find out more about the Care to Learn scheme and how to apply on the Gov.uk website", :cy=>"Cewch wybod mwy am y cynllun Care to Learn a sut mae gwneud cais ar wefan Gov.uk", :url=>"https://www.gov.uk/care-to-learn"}, 133=>{:en=>"Ask your college about help from the Financial Contingency Fund", :cy=>"Gofynnwch i’ch coleg am help gan y Gronfa Ariannol Wrth Gefn", :url=>""}, 134=>{:en=>"Apply directly to your college for financial support  from the Childcare Fund", :cy=>"Apply directly to your college for financial support  from the Childcare Fund", :url=>""}, 135=>{:en=>"In England contact Studentparents", :cy=>"In England contact Studentparents", :url=>"http://www.studentparents.org/student-finance.aspx"}, 136=>{:en=>"In Wales contact Student Finance Wales", :cy=>"", :url=>"http://www.studentfinancewales.co.uk/portal/page?_pageid=616,6200692&_dad=portal&_schema=PORTAL"}, 137=>{:en=>"In Scotland, contact Student Awards Agency for Scotland", :cy=>"In Scotland, contact Student Awards Agency for Scotland", :url=>"http://www.saas.gov.uk/"}, 138=>{:en=>"In Northern Ireland contact Student Finance NI", :cy=>"In Northern Ireland contact Student Finance NI", :url=>"http://www.studentfinanceni.co.uk/portal/page?_pageid=54,1265897&_dad=portal&_schema=PORTAL"}, 139=>{:en=>"Find your local Jobcentre Plus", :cy=>"", :url=>"http://los.direct.gov.uk/default.aspx?type=1&lang=en"}, 140=>{:en=>"If you live in Northern Ireland, contact your local Jobs and Benefits Office ", :cy=>"If you live in Northern Ireland, contact your local Jobs and Benefits Office ", :url=>"http://www.nidirect.gov.uk/social-security-jobs-and-benefits-offices"}, 141=>{:en=>"Find out more about Statutory Paternity Pay on the Gov.uk website ", :cy=>"Cael gwybod mwy am Dâl Tadolaeth Statudol ar wefan Gov.uk", :url=>"https://www.gov.uk/paternity-pay"}, 142=>{:en=>"The easiest way to tell your employer is to download and complete form SC3 'Becoming a parent' from the HM 